# Phase 16 — UI Design Contract (Cursor)

> Visual and interaction contract for UI Restoration phase. Applies Cursor's warm minimalist design language — warm cream canvas, orange accent, atmospheric shadows, oklab borders — across all frontend components.

---

## Design System

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Tool | shadcn (base-ui primitives) + custom CVA components |
| Preset | Cursor — warm minimalism with atmospheric depth |
| Component library | @base-ui/react (shadcn wrappers) |
| Icon library | Lucide React (`lucide-react`) |
| Font | Inter Variable (`cv01`, `ss03`) + Fira Code (mono) |
| Philosophy | Warm surfaces, diffused shadows, oklab borders, hover-to-crimson |

---

## Spacing Scale

8px base system with sub-8px fine scale:

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| xs | 4px | Icon gaps, inline padding |
