## Component Stylings

### Buttons

**Primary (Warm Surface)**
- Background: `var(--secondary)` (#ebeae5 light / #2d2c26 dark)
- Text: `var(--foreground)` (#26251e light / #f2f1ed dark)
- Radius: 8px (rounded-lg)
- Hover: text shifts to `var(--destructive)` (#cf2d56) — Cursor's signature hover-to-crimson
- Focus: `rgba(0,0,0,0.1) 0 4px 12px` shadow

**Accent Primary (Brand Orange)**
- Background: `var(--primary)` (#f54e00)
- Text: `var(--primary-foreground)` (#ffffff)
- Radius: 8px
- Hover: opacity 0.9 or background shift to `#e54700`
- Use: CTAs, submit buttons, key actions

**Ghost**
- Background: transparent
- Text: `var(--muted-foreground)`
- Hover: `var(--muted)` background + `var(--foreground)` text

**Destructive**
- Background: `var(--destructive/10)`
- Text: `var(--destructive)`
- Hover: `var(--destructive/20)` background

**Pill / Tag**
- Background: `var(--muted)`
- Text: `var(--muted-foreground)`
- Radius: full pill (9999px)
- Hover: text shifts to `var(--destructive)` (Cursor pattern)

### Cards & Containers
- Background: `var(--card)` (#ffffff light / #222119 dark)
- Border: `1px solid var(--border)` — warm tinted
- Radius: 8px (rounded-lg) standard, 4px compact, 10px featured
- Shadow: ambient (Level 2) for floating cards, none for inline cards
- Hover: shadow intensification (ambient -> elevated)

### Inputs & Forms
- Background: transparent or `var(--muted)`
- Text: `var(--foreground)`
- Border: `1px solid var(--border)`
- Focus: border shifts to `var(--ring)` (#f54e00) with warm focus shadow
- Radius: 8px (rounded-lg)

### Navigation
- Background: `var(--background)` — warm cream/dark
- Active nav: `var(--primary)` text or left border accent
- Hover: warm crimson text shift on interactive nav items
- Sidebar: `var(--sidebar)` background with warm borders

