## Token Migration Rules

Rules for converting hardcoded color classes to semantic tokens:

| Hardcoded Pattern | Semantic Token | Notes |
|-------------------|---------------|-------|
| `text-slate-900`, `text-gray-900`, `text-slate-950` | `text-foreground` | Primary text |
| `text-slate-600`, `text-gray-600`, `text-slate-500` | `text-muted-foreground` | Secondary/muted text |
| `text-slate-400`, `text-gray-400`, `text-slate-300` | `text-muted-foreground` | Tertiary text |
| `text-white`, `dark:text-white` | `text-foreground` (dark) or `text-primary-foreground` (on accent bg) | Context-dependent |
| `bg-white`, `dark:bg-slate-950` | `bg-card` | Card/panel surfaces |
| `bg-slate-50`, `bg-gray-50` | `bg-muted` | Muted backgrounds |
| `border-slate-200`, `border-gray-200` | `border-border` | Standard borders |
| `dark:border-slate-800`, `dark:border-slate-700` | `border-border` | Dark mode borders |
| `bg-slate-100`, `bg-gray-100` | `bg-secondary` | Secondary backgrounds |
| `rounded-2xl`, `rounded-[28px]` | `rounded-lg` (8px) | Cursor uses 8px base radius |
| `material-symbols-outlined` | Lucide React icon component | Replace with equivalent Lucide icon |
| `AlgoMaster` | `CodeNexus` | Brand rename |

